value: Breeds in northern Asia at the mouth of the Yenessei, in western Taimyr, Cape Bolschoi Baranov and on the New Siberian Islands. On migration occurs throughout Europe and Asia; winters in Africa, Mada- gascar, India, Burma, Malay Archipelago, and Australia.
